                "invention-title": [
                    "Fixed bed device for synthesizing acetaldehyde by utilizing solar high-power condensation and preparation method",
                    "一种利用太阳能高倍聚光合成乙醛的固定床装置及制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a fixed bed device for synthesizing acetaldehyde by utilizing solar high-power condensation. A first condenser is condensed on a photovoltaic cell and is connected with an electrical storage device; the sodium chloride solution electrolysis device is connected with the electrical storage device and electrolyzes a sodium chloride solution, the sodium chloride solution electrolysis device is communicated with the palladium chloride high-temperature oxidation-reduction synthesis chamber through the first hydrogen adsorption fixed bed device, and the second condenser condenses light in the palladium chloride high-temperature oxidation-reduction synthesis chamber; the water electrolysis device is connected with the electrical storage device, electrolyzes water and is communicated with the second hydrogen adsorption fixed bed device; an ethylene raw material container; the palladium chloride high-temperature oxidation-reduction synthesis chamber is communicated with the acetaldehyde synthesis chamber to provide a palladium chloride catalyst, the second hydrogen adsorption fixed bed device is communicated with the acetaldehyde synthesis chamber to provide oxygen, the ethylene raw material container is communicated with the acetaldehyde synthesis chamber to provide ethylene, and acetaldehyde is prepared from ethylene and oxygen under the action of the palladium chloride catalyst. According to the method, acetaldehyde is prepared through solar photoelectric and photo-thermal, and the problems of energy consumption and catalyst cost are solved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种利用太阳能高倍聚光合成乙醛的固定床装置，第一聚光镜聚光于光伏电池连接蓄电装置；氯化钠溶液电解装置与蓄电装置连接并电解氯化钠溶液，氯化钠溶液电解装置通过第一吸附氢气固定床装置与氯化钯高温氧化还原合成室连通，第二聚光镜聚光于氯化钯高温氧化还原合成室；电解水装置与蓄电装置连接并电解水，与第二吸附氢气固定床装置连通；乙烯原料容器；氯化钯高温氧化还原合成室与乙醛合成室连通提供氯化钯催化剂，第二吸附氢气固定床装置与乙醛合成室连通提供氧气，乙烯原料容器与乙醛合成室连通提供乙烯，乙烯与氧气在氯化钯催化剂作用下制备乙醛。本发明利用太阳能光电光热制取乙醛，克服能源消耗和催化剂的成本问题。"
                }
